br.com.gamemods.nbtmanipulator

Class NbtList.Companion

  • br.com.gamemods.nbtmanipulator.NbtList.Companion
  • Enclosing class:
    NbtList<T extends NbtTag>

    public static class NbtList.Companion

    Contains useful methods to create class NbtLists from Java.

    Kotlin users may call list(1,2,3).toNbtList() or similar methods.
